section.para:
For creating a new person in the system, you will be working with the trackedEntityInstances resource. A template payload can be seen
        below:{
    "trackedEntity": "tracked-entity-id",
    "orgUnit": "org-unit-id",
    "attributes": [ {
        "attribute": "attribute-id",
        "value": "attribute-value"
    } ]
}

 For example, let us create a new instance of a person tracked entity and specify its
        first name and last name
        attributes:{
  "trackedEntity": "nEenWmSyUEp",
  "orgUnit": "DiszpKrYNg8",
  "attributes": [
    {
      "attribute": "w75KJ2mc4zz",
